{"title":"Kali 安装网易云音乐","slug":"kali/kali_wangyiyun","date":"2018-04-22T14:56:13.978Z","updated":"2018-04-22T14:58:02.846Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/kali/kali_wangyiyun.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"首先，进入网易云音乐官网下载安装包。<br>","covers":null,"content":"<p>首先，进入网易云音乐官网下载安装包。<br><a id=\"more\"></a></p>\n<h2 id=\"下载\"><a href=\"#下载\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下载\"></a>下载</h2><p><a href=\"http://music.163.com/#/download\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">http://music.163.com/#/download</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"安装\"><a href=\"#安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装\"></a>安装</h2><p>在下载的文件下打开终端，或进入网易云下载的位置</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">root@Crazy:~<span class=\"comment\"># dpkg -i netease-cloud-music-1.0.0-2_amd64_deepin15.deb</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>如报错，解决办法</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">root@Crazy:~<span class=\"comment\"># apt-get -f install</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">root@Crazy:~<span class=\"comment\"># dpkg -i netease-cloud-music-1.0.0-2_amd64_deepin15.deb</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"root-运行网易云音乐\"><a href=\"#root-运行网易云音乐\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"root 运行网易云音乐\"></a>root 运行网易云音乐</h2><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">root@Crazy:~<span class=\"comment\"># vim /usr/share/applications/netease-cloud-music.desktop</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>修改Exec=netease-cloud-music %U</p>\n<p>为Exec=netease-cloud-music %U –no-sandbox</p>\n<p>补充：<br>vim<br>1.切换至插入模式（Insert mode）才能编辑文件—按字母 i<br>2.编辑完成后按ESC退出编辑<br>3.输入：wq (保存并退出)<br>    ：q! (不保存退出)</p>\n",